rows.label: qst202605_msg0003
rows.name: So this is where you were.

rows.label: qst202605_msg0004
rows.name: We've been looking all over for you.

rows.label: qst202605_msg0006
rows.name:
Did you fly away alone at that time
so as not to cause us any trouble?

rows.label: qst202605_msg0008
rows.name:
But it seems you're all
right now. That strange
feeling from before is gone.

rows.label: qst202605_msg0009
rows.name: Yes, you seem to be your usual self.

rows.label: qst202605_msg0013
rows.name:
You are worried about going
berserk, are you not?

rows.label: qst202605_msg0015
rows.name:
But that was our fault...[ML:Dash ] it
wasn't your fault, Ten'i.

rows.label: qst202605_msg0016
rows.name:
That's right. It's not a problem
for you to worry about alone.
